r Körperschaftsteuer und Gewerbesteuer wurden signifikant ergänzt.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 4aHandelsrecht. 4aPersonengesellschaft. 4aSteuerrecht. 4aStille Gesellschaft. 4aZivilrecht. 7aLAW / Commercial / General.2bisacsh1 aBlaurock, Uwe, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKauffeld, Hans-Georg, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aLamprecht, Philipp, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aLevedag, Christian, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aTeufel, Tobias, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aWachter, Thomas, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Law 2020z9783110704587oZDB-23-DGC40uhttps://doi.org/10.9785/978350438636840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783504386368423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783504386368.jpg  a978-3-11-069629-5  DG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2b2020  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGCb2020  aZDB-23-DGGb2020